MODIFICATIONS made by fern, as required by Apache-2.0 section 4(b):

  - Import paths repointed from HeroUI's tree to fern's.
  - Internationalisation removed. fern's docs are single-locale, so
    `useI18n()` lookups were replaced with literal English strings, the
    `<I18nLabel>` component was replaced with its text, and
    ui/language-toggle.tsx was dropped along with the two `{!!i18n && …}`
    blocks that rendered it.

